{"word":"H1239 - בָּקַר - bâqar - baw-kar - Inquire","slug":"H1239","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בָּקַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>bâqar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>baw-kar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Inquire"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05E7;&#x05E8; - ba&#x0302;qar</b> - <i>baw-kar'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>plough</i>, or (generally) <i>break</i> forth, that is, (figuratively) to <i>inspect</i>, <i>admire</i>, <i>care for</i>, <i>consider: - </i>(make) inquire (-ry), (make) search, seek out."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1241\">H1241</a>, <a href=\"#/H1242\">H1242</a>, <a href=\"#/H1243\">H1243</a>, <a href=\"#/H1244\">H1244</a>, <a href=\"#/H951\">H951</a>"}]}